ing: 1 frozen banana, partially thawed and mashed
1/2 cup milk, or more to taste
des: "It doesn't have any ice cream but tastes like a milkshake! This is a recipe that my uncle told me about. At first I thought, 'Gross! That sounds terrible!' As it turns out everyone in my family loves it; even my picky sister who hates bananas! This is a recipe for when the kids say, 'Mom can we go to SonicÂ®? We want a milkshake!' And instead the kids can eat a delicious, healthy, and filling summer snack. The most important direction of all: Enjoy!"
ins: Mix banana and milk together in a cup or bowl until desired consistency is reached.
